creator: vibons
descriptionHtml:
The Journey app helps you develop skills with actionable guidance and continuous follow-up.  

As an employee, Journey helps you to develop your skills by
* Assessing the crucial skills, which will have the biggest impact on your career,
* Building effective development plans, which includes on-the-job assignments, mentors, and training,
* Receiving just-in-time guidance with relevant content,
* Tracking your progress with follow-ups.

As a manager, Journey allows you to develop your subordinates by
* Identifying business-critical skills,
* Helping them to create effective development plans,
* Tracking their progress,
* Evaluating the overall success of your team's development.

Note: Your organization must authorize access to the Journey mobile app.

* Assessing the crucial skills, which will have the biggest impact on your career,
* Building effective development plans, which includes on-the-job assignments, mentors, and training,
* Receiving just-in-time guidance with relevant content,
* Tracking your progress with follow-ups.

As a manager, Journey allows you to develop your subordinates by
* Identifying business-critical skills,
* Helping them to create effective development plans,
* Tracking their progress,
* Evaluating the overall success of your team's development.

Note: Your organization must authorize access to the Journey mobile app.
